title: Find a home, the easy way - Home in Port Orchard. 3 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: ["Peaceful and quiet on over an acre with a territorial view is what captures this home's essence.", ' You are a short drive to the Southworth-Seattle fast ferry, which puts you in Seattle in 30 minutes.', 'This immense rambler has a spacious living room with fireplace that looks out over the acreage.', 'The primary bedroom has a large, walk-in closet & full, private bath.', 'There is a massive wood deck which nicely takes in the territorial view & lends itself well for entertainment.', 'The flooring has all been updated with hardwood laminate flooring.', 'The kitchen has been updated, as well.', "For the owner who desires water skiing and lake activities, Long Lake is just a stone's throw away.", 'There are 2 outbuildings in addition to the 3-car attached garage.', '***Please Text & Call', 'show contact info', 'For More Details & Pics***']
